ill says of the label'sguayabera-inspired Cuban shirt.WATCH Fayad & Co. founder Andre Fayad, whose Miami-based business does a brisk trade inbespoke guayaberas, likens thestyle's current position to where the Western shirt had been several seasons ago.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_Drake\", \"score\": 0.9999751660625893, \"rank\": 2.4833145078671472e-05, \"text\": \"Drake\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_Drake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_Drake\"}, {\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Hill_Jeweller\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 2.0472304789563764e-12, \"text\": \"Michael Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Hill_Jeweller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Hill_Jeweller\"}, {\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"score\": 0.9368565387926916, \"rank\": 0.06739053709467942, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cubans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the embroidery\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"the camp collar\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"our fish-eye mother\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"pearl buttons\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"an updated take\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"a high summer staple\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"WATCH\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"Fayad & Co. founder Andre Fayad\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"whose Miami-based business\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"a brisk trade\", \"from