", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our interpretation\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"a guayabera\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"a guayabera\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Latin culture, a guayabera is very formal.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3447, \"end\": 3452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\", \"score\": 0.9653073536296191, \"rank\": 0.0346899330204846, \"text\": \"Latin\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a guayabera\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's what you wear to a wedding\\u2026 you typically do not wear a guayabera as a casual thing, because it just looks a bit off.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wedding\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3521}, {\"ngram\": \"a guayabera\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"a casual thing\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so, I wanted to have that same kind of playful inspiration yet have something you'd wear with a pair of swim trunks or trousers.\\\"\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that same kind\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3652}, {\"ngram\": \"playful inspiration\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3675}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"swim trunks\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"trousers\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Atlanta-based retailerSid Mashburnstocks both aguayabera shirtand a guayabera-adjacent \\\"minimal riff\\\" dubbed theMarquez, which features four pockets but no decorative details.\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Atlanta-based retailerSid Mashburnstocks\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"aguayabera shirtand\", \"from\": 3798, \"to\": 3817}, {\"ngram\": \"a guayabera-adjacent \\\"minimal riff\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3852}, {\"ngram\": \"theMarquez\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3871}, {\"ngram\": \"four pockets\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"no decorative details\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And though the label's guayabera is more traditional in appearance-right down to the hem pockets that can be found in a black-and-white photo of Gary Cooper wearing the style-the designer is transparent about its breaks with convention.\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 4164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4073, \"end\": 4084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Cooper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.633935685749546e-41, \"text\": \"Gary Cooper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Cooper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Cooper\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the label's guayabera\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3960}, {\"ngram\": \"appearance-right\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"the hem pockets\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"a black-and-white photo\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4069}, {\"ngram\": \"the style\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4102}, {\"ngram\": \"the designer\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4115}, {\"ngram\": \"its breaks\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4147}, {\"ngram\": \"convention\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some purists may not be so into our version\\u2026 we have taken some liberties,\\\" Mashburn tellsRobb Report.\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some purists\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4179}, {\"ngram\": \"our version\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"some liberties\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For instance, ours does not have the decorative embroidery that some guys love, and it fits a bit closer to the body than some-it's relaxed but not oversized.\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"the decorative embroidery\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"some guys\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4343}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the traditional ones too; it's just not what we make.\\\"\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the traditional ones\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While donning a conventional guayabera could make the wearer unknowingly overdressed, the style carries other pratfalls, too.\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a conventional guayabera\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4530}, {\"ngram\": \"the wearer\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4552}, {\"ngram\": \"the style\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4587}, {\"ngram\": \"other pratfalls\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fayad often dissuades clients from ordering white linen iterations with short sleeves for a very particular reason.\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fayad\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4623}, {\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4647}, {\"ngram\": \"white linen iterations\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4684}, {\"ngram\": \"short sleeves\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"a very particular reason\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Walk down Lincoln road,\\\" he says, referring to the restaurant-heavy strip in Miami's South Beach neighborhood, \\\"and all the waiters are wearing white linen guayaberas with short sleeves.\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4746, \"end\": 4753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"score\": 0.7658351084273107, \"rank\": 0.3057641116161674, \"text\": \"Lincoln\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\"}, {\"begin\": 4813, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.004196066163609e-14, \"text\": \"Miami\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miami\"}, {\"begin\": 4821, \"end\": 4832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Beach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8563370703478024e-24, \"text\": \"South Beach\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Beach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Beach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the restaurant-heavy strip\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4809}, {\"ngram\": \"all the waiters\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4867}, {\"ngram\": \"white linen guayaberas\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4902}, {\"ngram\": \"short sleeves\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has become like the white dinner jacket for restaurants, and sometimes you do not want to do that.\\\"\", \"from\": 4923, \"to\": 5025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the white dinner jacket\", \"from\": 4942, \"to\": 4965}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 4981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Fayad points patrons toward more creative commissions, like a charcoal linen guayabera that might be worn in the evening with a lighter-colored trouser.\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fayad\", \"from\": 5036, \"to\": 5041}, {\"ngram\": \"patrons\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"more creative commissions\", \"from\": 5064, \"to\": 5089}, {\"ngram\": \"a charcoal linen guayabera\", \"from\": 5096, \"to\": 5122}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5156}, {\"ngram\": \"a lighter-colored trouser\", \"from\": 5162, \"to\": 5187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Styling-wise, He's also had clients request guayaberas with a shorter hem, or even concealed button plackets for a sleeker look.\", \"from\": 5189, \"to\": 5317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clients\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5224}, {\"ngram\": \"guayaberas\", \"from\": 5233, \"to\": 5243}, {\"ngram\": \"a shorter hem\", \"from\": 5249, \"to\": 5262}, {\"ngram\": \"button plackets\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"a sleeker look\", \"from\": 5302, \"to\": 5316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am always open to traditional with a little bit of a twist or making it your own,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5413, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5369}, {\"ngram\": \"a twist\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the guayabera is indeed on the same trajectory as the Western shirt, we are likely to see it in many new cuts, colors, and fabrications in the years to come.\", \"from\": 5415, \"to\": 5575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guayabera\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5431}, {\"ngram\": \"the same trajectory\", \"from\": 5445, \"to\": 5464}, {\"ngram\": \"the Western shirt\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5485}, {\"ngram\": \"many new cuts\", \"from\": 5514, \"to\": 5527}, {\"ngram\": \"colors\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5535}, {\"ngram\": \"fabrications\", \"from\": 5541, \"to\": 5553}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just do not forget where the style came from-and try not to look as if you have strayed from a wedding reception.\", \"from\": 5576, \"to\": 5689, \"entities\": [], 